    "body": "### Neovim Version\n\nNVIM v0.5.0\n\n### Operating system/version:\n\nUbuntu 21.04\n\n### Terminal name/version:\n\nKonsole 20.12.3\n\n### TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nappimage\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nFirst change the terminal's color scheme to use a light background.\r\n\r\nThen:\r\n\r\n```vim\r\nnvim -u NORC\r\n\" Confirm background=light\r\n:set background?\r\n\" Run Neovim within Neovim\r\n:term nvim\r\n\" Focus inner Neovim (alternatively could press \"i\")\r\n:startinsert\r\n\" Check background\r\n:set background?\r\n```\r\n\n\n### Vim\n\nThe expected behavior is encountered when running 1) Vim within Vim, 2) Neovim within Vim, or 3) Vim within Neovim.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\n`background=light` within the inner Neovim.\n\n### Actual behavior\n\n`background=dark` within the inner Neovim.",
